data.description: Bridge Harbor Community is waiting for you.  This home at 4 bedrooms and 2 bath was the Model Home of the new Community, and additional bells and whistles was added.  The Ryder Floor-plan gives you an open floor feeling with abundance of room throughout to include wide hallways etc.   Home sits on a corner lot and built in 2021, thus still giving you the new look feel.  Entering the home, you are greeted by traditional 8' foot ceilings and vinyl  sheet flooring throughout the main areas.  The  large kitchen overlooks the great room and dinning area.  Split bedrooms with the master on the other side of the home, and a large laundry room.   You have 3 additional bedrooms and can convert one to an office.  The family room flows right into the fully privacy fenced back yard with a covered patio.  Low HOA fees includes a Community pool for the kids, sidewalks and lighting and Gazebo.   Home is located near Tyndall A.F.B., shopping and restaurants.
